				p Prey - the apartment
		.tip.fragment.bottom-20.right-450
			img.height-700(src=imgAssets+'upgrade.jpg')
+frameInbox('Principle #4 - The player is constantly learning')
	div
		ul
			li.fragment <span class="highlight">learn - play- challenge - surprise</span> loop
			li.fragment every new challenge will require the player to use his/her equipment in new ways
		.center.flex-row.mt-100
			figure.mx-10.fragment
				img.height-450(src=imgAssets+'principle03_doom.jpg')
				p Doom - picking up BFG
			figure.mx-10.fragment
				img.height-450(src=imgAssets+'principle03_zelda.jpg')
				p The Legend of Zelda - new equipment
+frameInbox('Principle #5 - The game introduces surprise elements')
	div
		ul
			li.fragment flip existing paradigms to boost the game experience
			li.fragment fun is created through uncertainty and surprise
		.center.flex-row.mt-100
